<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.7.2">
<l>cekkariṭai nuṉikkompil tōṉṟumci ṟupiṟai muḷaippōla</l>
<l>nakkacentu varvāyttiṇ ṇaimītē naḷirveṇpal muḷaiyilaka</l>
<l>vakkuvaṭa muṭuttāmait tālipūṇ ṭavaṉan tacayaṉaṉ</l>
<l>takkamāma ṇivaṇṇaṉ vācutēvaṉ taḷarnaṭai naṭavāṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will Vāsudeva,</l>
<l rend="indent">he with the complexion of fitting dark sapphires,</l>
<l rend="indent">he who sleeps on Ananta,</l>
<l rend="indent">he who wears a tortoise necklace [and] a string of bones,</l>
<l>not come with a tottering walk</l>
<l>while the tender shoot of his cool white tooth shines</l>
<l>on the surface of the mound of [his] smiling red coral mouth</l>
<l>resembling a beam of the small crescent moon</l>
<l>that appears on the tip of a branch in the middle of the red evening sky?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
